{"tid":245263,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[機戰] 呢排重玩完Z1","createTime":"2017-05-16T06:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T05:39:59.000Z","uid":17954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed45257428ef55913ead7c699bb83f40467dee84","tid":245263,"uid":17954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"Z1真係集百家大成既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難易度適中，即使有改機體，前中段衝SR都有一定難度。 <del>後段一架 ニルヴァーシュ無雙</del><br />\n<br />\n配合改良左既3人小隊制<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>後段一架 ニルヴァーシュ無雙</del><br />\n<br />\nseedd 劇情完整之餘，if亦都寫得好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n55 話Meer既劇情配合 君は僕に似ている<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重有真對議長所講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「俺は&hellip;誰かに望まれた生き方より、自分の信じた事を選んだんです！ だから、人の心や自由を奪うデスティニープランは認めません！」<br />\n「&hellip;だけど、俺は生きます！ 誰に何を言われようと、俺は俺だから！ デュランダル議長！それを認めないのなら、俺はあなたと戦います！！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜打後既都開始偏易，係養成同難度拎唔返平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>後段一架 ニルヴァーシュ無雙</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新既V的確唔錯，不過冇小隊制感覺冇咁好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74011ed42dec36cf427dbe09dc68ef9b84a29ac2","tid":245263,"uid":65556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"其實暫時見親啲人對小隊編制模式既意見都好極端，我自己就偏向小隊制多啲"},{"pid":"83616bee64bc4cd3986fd1144fc1dec835b2d0c6","tid":245263,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"唔係紅蓮勁啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc7c9f9db106b135b4fceaa4e4d554ab015644","tid":245263,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係紅蓮勁啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2先有"},{"pid":"6f7d8e48fcc4ea